jannah","tag-punishment-al-uqubah","tag-warning-al-nudhr","tag-women-al-nisa"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-8Ob","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":13588,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/04\/15\/talaq-worst-of-halal\/","url_meta":{"origin":33863,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Talaq: Worst of permissible matters is divorce","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 15, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Umar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe most hateful of lawful matters to Allah is divorce.\u201d Source: Sunan Ab\u012b D\u0101w\u016bd 2172 Grade: Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Suyuti \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064f\u0645\u064e\u0631\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0645\u064e \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0652\u063a\u064e\u0636\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0652\u062d\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":36374,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/05\/28\/who-in-paradise\/","url_meta":{"origin":33863,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Jannah: Prophets, martyrs, children in Paradise","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 28, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Hasna' bint Mu'awiyah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe Prophet is in Paradise, the martyrs are in Paradise, the young children who die are in Paradise, and the infant buried alive is in Paradise.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 2521 Grade: Hasan (fair) according\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":37863,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2022\/06\/12\/mindful-friday-khutbah\/","url_meta":{"origin":33863,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Jumu\u2019ah: Have presence at sermon, be near to Imam","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 12, 2022","format":false,"excerpt":"Samurah ibn Jundub reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cBe present at the sermon and come close to the Imam. Verily, a man continues to distance himself until he is delayed from Paradise, even though he will eventually enter it.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":843,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/06\/08\/cruel-not-enter-paradise\/","url_meta":{"origin":33863,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Cruelty: Harsh, mean people do not enter Paradise","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 8, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Harithah ibn Wahb reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cNeither the haughty, nor the cruel, will enter Paradise.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 4801 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Arna'ut \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u062d\u064e\u0627\u0631\u0650\u062b\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0647\u0652\u0628\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0645\u064e \u0644\u064e\u0627 \u064a\u064e\u062f\u0652\u062e\u064f\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0652\u062c\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0651\u0629\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":1982,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/02\/21\/break-peace-treaty-no-jannah\/","url_meta":{"origin":33863,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Covenants: Whoever betrays peace treaty not enter Paradise","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 21, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Bakrah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever kills a person protected by a treaty without a just cause, Allah has forbidden Paradise for him.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 2760 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Arna'ut \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0628\u064e\u0643\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &qu